    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Scissors, which comprise a pair of pivoted blades attached to handles, designed for tasks involved in sewing, including cutting thread and clipping seams. For scissors to cut lengths of fabric, use "sewing shears."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
